file.name: non-unique-enum-values.yml
file.content:
---
# An example where there are enum values that will map to duplicate names
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Example
  version: '1.0.1'
paths:
  /test1:
    get:
      parameters:
      - name: param1
        in: query
        schema:
          type: string
          enum: [0, 1, 2, 3, -1]
      responses:
        200:
          description: OK

Error: parse: paths: /test1: get: : parameters: parse parameter "param1": schema: parse enum values: parse value "0": expected type "string", got "number"
